    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Events or activities of finding out or becoming aware of something that had been lost, forgotten, or previously unknown. Includes the finding of archaeological objects, lost buildings, places; also includes the action of bringing to light substances, scientific phenoma, and other things that were previously unknown.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
